00:00:07.642 --> 00:00:11.078 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Dio] North latitude,
28 degrees 24 minutes.

00:00:11.111 --> 00:00:14.782 position:27% line:83% align:start
West longitude,
80 degrees 36 minutes.

00:00:14.816 --> 00:00:19.319 position:10% line:83% align:start
Go there and wait patiently
for the next new moon.

00:00:19.353 --> 00:00:22.624 position:30% line:83% align:start
And that place
is at Cape Canaveral.

00:00:22.657 --> 00:00:24.559 position:10% line:89% align:start
Space Center, to be precise.

00:00:24.592 --> 00:00:26.628 position:21% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music]

00:00:26.661 --> 00:00:28.696 position:13% line:89% align:start
The time is the new moon.

00:00:28.730 --> 00:00:30.698 position:24% line:89% align:start
Six days from now.

00:00:30.732 --> 00:00:32.000 position:19% line:89% align:start
Let's face the facts,

00:00:32.032 --> 00:00:34.602 position:19% line:83% align:start
my old man would never
let that priest get away.

00:00:34.636 --> 00:00:36.270 position:16% line:89% align:start
My name is Jolyne Cujoh!

00:00:36.303 --> 00:00:39.439 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's up to me to seal what
that bastard just obtained.

00:00:39.473 --> 00:00:43.310 position:7% line:83% align:start
It's a prison break. And we're
about to leave any minute.

00:00:43.343 --> 00:00:45.312 position:33% line:83% align:start
Then I think
you gotta take me with you.

00:00:51.451 --> 00:00:54.956 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Ermes] So we're finally saying
adios to the Aquarium, huh?

00:00:54.989 --> 00:00:56.724 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Jolyne] I thought this place
was horrendous

00:00:56.758 --> 00:00:57.825 position:10% line:89% align:start
when I first got locked up.

00:00:58.760 --> 00:01:00.060 position:10% line:89% align:start
But now that I look back...

00:01:01.663 --> 00:01:03.031 position:21% line:89% align:start
[both] It's clear...

00:01:03.063 --> 00:01:05.033 position:13% line:89% align:start
it really was a shithole.

00:01:05.065 --> 00:01:07.100 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Emporio panting]
So that's the gas station.

00:01:07.802 --> 00:01:09.436 position:16% line:89% align:start
And this is a bus stop.

00:01:09.469 --> 00:01:12.006 position:33% line:83% align:start
Are we gonna
be taking the bus here?

00:01:12.040 --> 00:01:14.441 position:21% line:83% align:start
I've never actually
been on one before.

00:01:14.474 --> 00:01:16.844 position:24% line:83% align:start
You realize we're
escaped convicts, right?

00:01:16.878 --> 00:01:19.279 position:10% line:83% align:start
We'll get caught the second
we set foot on the bus.

00:01:19.313 --> 00:01:21.549 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yeah, but if we're going
after the priest

00:01:21.583 --> 00:01:24.217 position:10% line:83% align:start
there's no way we'll be able
to catch up to him on foot.

00:01:24.251 --> 00:01:26.821 position:19% line:83% align:start
We know, we just have
to find another way.

00:01:26.854 --> 00:01:28.590 position:10% line:89% align:start
[dramatic revelation music]

00:01:33.828 --> 00:01:35.697 position:30% line:89% align:start
[theme music]

00:03:09.123 --> 00:03:10.490 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia] Back up,
Weather Forecast.

00:03:11.224 --> 00:03:12.492 position:24% line:89% align:start
What did you say?

00:03:13.027 --> 00:03:14.862 position:27% line:89% align:start
Jolyne is gone.

00:03:14.896 --> 00:03:18.666 position:19% line:83% align:start
She's no longer in the
women's ward or in her cell.

00:03:18.700 --> 00:03:22.302 position:13% line:83% align:start
I can feel it in the air.
She's finally free.

00:03:22.335 --> 00:03:24.706 position:13% line:83% align:start
My guess is she pulled off
a prison break.

00:03:27.542 --> 00:03:28.142 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:03:28.176 --> 00:03:29.677 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia] Hey, hang on.

00:03:29.711 --> 00:03:30.444 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia gasps]

00:03:33.081 --> 00:03:35.717 position:5% line:89% align:start
A birthmark shaped like a star.

00:03:38.052 --> 00:03:39.153 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Weather] Hmm.

00:03:39.187 --> 00:03:41.455 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia]
Who the hell are you?

00:03:41.488 --> 00:03:44.324 position:13% line:83% align:start
I've seen that star-shaped
birthmark somewhere before

00:03:44.357 --> 00:03:47.360 position:7% line:83% align:start
in the same place on the back
of The Green Baby's neck.

00:03:47.394 --> 00:03:50.031 position:27% line:83% align:start
And supposedly,
Jolyne's father bears a mark

00:03:50.064 --> 00:03:52.232 position:10% line:89% align:start
that shares the same shape.

00:03:52.265 --> 00:03:55.235 position:16% line:83% align:start
You'd better think hard
if you can't remember.

00:03:55.268 --> 00:03:57.939 position:13% line:83% align:start
How exactly did you end up
at Green Dolphin?

00:03:57.972 --> 00:03:59.707 position:13% line:89% align:start
Since you have no memory,

00:03:59.741 --> 00:04:01.843 position:16% line:83% align:start
does that mean it's safe
to assume that the priest

00:04:01.876 --> 00:04:04.411 position:13% line:83% align:start
extracted your memory disc
like all the others?

00:04:05.813 --> 00:04:09.416 position:30% line:83% align:start
He's my enemy.
That's all that I can tell you.

00:04:09.449 --> 00:04:12.352 position:13% line:83% align:start
I need to learn the truth,
so I'm breaking out of here

00:04:12.385 --> 00:04:14.321 position:16% line:89% align:start
to find him and end him.

00:04:15.757 --> 00:04:16.824 position:24% line:89% align:start
What will you do?

00:04:16.858 --> 00:04:19.060 position:30% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:04:19.093 --> 00:04:20.194 position:30% line:83% align:start
[radio anchor]
This just in.

00:04:20.228 --> 00:04:21.596 position:5% line:89% align:start
Two convicts have broken out of

00:04:21.629 --> 00:04:23.097 position:21% line:83% align:start
Green Dolphin Street
State Prison

00:04:23.131 --> 00:04:24.464 position:7% line:89% align:start
and are currently on the run.

00:04:25.066 --> 00:04:26.399 position:16% line:89% align:start
The escaped convicts are

00:04:26.433 --> 00:04:28.836 position:33% line:83% align:start
Jolyne Cujoh
and Ermes Costello.

00:04:28.870 --> 00:04:31.271 position:19% line:83% align:start
Photos of the two have
been released to the public.

00:04:31.304 --> 00:04:34.208 position:19% line:83% align:start
Please contact us with
any information.

00:04:34.242 --> 00:04:36.043 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
Jolyne, it sounds as though

00:04:36.077 --> 00:04:38.045 position:27% line:83% align:start
you've defeated
Mew Mew's Stand,

00:04:38.079 --> 00:04:39.914 position:24% line:83% align:start
and you're intent
on finding me.

00:04:40.982 --> 00:04:42.817 position:30% line:89% align:start
[car rattling]

00:04:44.852 --> 00:04:46.486 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:46.521 --> 00:04:48.321 position:10% line:83% align:start
-Why'd the car stop moving?
-[car engine rumbling]

00:04:48.355 --> 00:04:50.825 position:10% line:83% align:start
There's still plenty of gas
in the tank.

00:04:50.858 --> 00:04:53.161 position:21% line:83% align:start
Something like this
has never happened.

00:04:53.194 --> 00:04:55.428 position:24% line:83% align:start
I always take care
of my vehicle.

00:04:55.462 --> 00:04:56.363 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi gasps]

00:04:59.233 --> 00:04:59.967 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:05:00.001 --> 00:05:01.836 position:19% line:89% align:start
[car engine rumbling]

00:05:06.541 --> 00:05:08.276 position:5% line:89% align:start
I've got some bad news, Father.

00:05:08.308 --> 00:05:11.245 position:10% line:83% align:start
This is as far as I can go.
My apologies.

00:05:11.279 --> 00:05:13.480 position:24% line:83% align:start
Please let me call
another cab for you.

00:05:13.514 --> 00:05:16.250 position:35% line:83% align:start
Thank you.
But there is no need.

00:05:16.284 --> 00:05:17.919 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm not in any hurry.

00:05:20.453 --> 00:05:22.757 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi] I have a week
until I'm born anew.

00:05:22.790 --> 00:05:25.593 position:30% line:83% align:start
And I'm still
in terrible physical condition.

00:05:25.626 --> 00:05:28.596 position:21% line:83% align:start
Just five more days
until the new moon.

00:05:28.629 --> 00:05:30.998 position:16% line:83% align:start
Guess I can wait it out
in this town.

00:05:31.032 --> 00:05:34.535 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'll need to keep Jolyne and
her friends away at all costs.

00:05:35.236 --> 00:05:37.205 position:16% line:89% align:start
[police sirens blaring]

00:05:37.238 --> 00:05:39.406 position:21% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music]

00:05:41.843 --> 00:05:44.579 position:27% line:83% align:start
[medic 1] Hurry,
he's going into cardiac arrest!

00:05:44.612 --> 00:05:46.446 position:5% line:83% align:start
[officer] This burglar was shot
in the leg by an officer

00:05:46.479 --> 00:05:48.883 position:13% line:83% align:start
then proceeded to jump off
the sixth floor of a building!

00:05:48.916 --> 00:05:50.885 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thrilling music]

00:05:55.756 --> 00:05:57.592 position:21% line:83% align:start
[medic 2] We've got
a biker punk over here!

00:05:57.625 --> 00:05:59.160 position:27% line:83% align:start
He drove against
the flow of traffic

00:05:59.193 --> 00:06:00.895 position:27% line:83% align:start
and slammed into
the median strip.

00:06:00.928 --> 00:06:02.296 position:35% line:83% align:start
[medic 3]
What the hell is going on?

00:06:02.330 --> 00:06:04.397 position:27% line:83% align:start
This drug addict
is going into shock!

00:06:08.736 --> 00:06:09.937 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ring clanging]

00:06:10.972 --> 00:06:12.874 position:21% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music]

00:06:12.907 --> 00:06:14.441 position:24% line:89% align:start
[blood squelching]

00:06:15.877 --> 00:06:17.979 position:33% line:89% align:start
[clattering]

00:06:26.053 --> 00:06:27.321 position:24% line:89% align:start
[officer screams]

00:06:27.355 --> 00:06:28.723 position:44% line:83% align:start
Hm.
[grunts]

00:06:28.756 --> 00:06:32.392 position:5% line:83% align:start
All right, listen up! Stay back
or the priest gets it!

00:06:33.493 --> 00:06:35.363 position:10% line:83% align:start
Careful, the druggy's awake
and out of control!

00:06:35.395 --> 00:06:37.598 position:24% line:83% align:start
Damn it! He cut me
with those scissors!

00:06:37.632 --> 00:06:40.368 position:27% line:83% align:start
Don't you point
those fucking guns at me!

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:42.136 position:38% line:83% align:start
No way!
There ain't no way in hell

00:06:42.169 --> 00:06:43.905 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'm gonna let you lock me up!

00:06:43.938 --> 00:06:45.706 position:16% line:89% align:start
[slow suspenseful music]

00:06:52.546 --> 00:06:55.116 position:24% line:83% align:start
Requesting backup.
There's a hostage situation

00:06:55.149 --> 00:06:56.384 position:27% line:89% align:start
at the hospital.

00:06:56.416 --> 00:06:58.119 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hey, shit for brains!

00:06:58.152 --> 00:06:59.654 position:5% line:89% align:start
What the hell did you just say?

00:06:59.687 --> 00:07:02.757 position:30% line:83% align:start
Are you stupid
or do you want this guy to die?

00:07:02.790 --> 00:07:05.092 position:7% line:89% align:start
You really pissed me off now!

00:07:05.126 --> 00:07:08.162 position:7% line:83% align:start
This fucker's throat is about
to get stabbed because of you!

00:07:09.263 --> 00:07:11.165 position:27% line:83% align:start
Earlier tonight,
I saw shooting stars

00:07:11.198 --> 00:07:13.167 position:24% line:89% align:start
in the sky above.

00:07:13.200 --> 00:07:15.468 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Three, to be precise.
-Huh?

00:07:15.503 --> 00:07:16.570 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
Just three.

00:07:16.604 --> 00:07:18.940 position:24% line:83% align:start
Clearly streaking
across the sky.

00:07:18.973 --> 00:07:20.374 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:07:20.408 --> 00:07:22.710 position:7% line:89% align:start
May I ask where you came from?

00:07:22.743 --> 00:07:24.378 position:13% line:89% align:start
Do you three have any idea

00:07:24.412 --> 00:07:25.913 position:13% line:83% align:start
-who it is you truly are?
-[Ungalo gasps]

00:07:28.416 --> 00:07:29.784 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:07:29.817 --> 00:07:30.985 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Ungalo gasps]

00:07:31.018 --> 00:07:33.521 position:13% line:83% align:start
-[Father Pucchi groaning]
-Shit, the psycho stabbed him!

00:07:33.554 --> 00:07:35.122 position:10% line:89% align:start
Wait a sec, that wasn't me!

00:07:35.156 --> 00:07:36.824 position:30% line:89% align:start
No, it wasn't,

00:07:36.857 --> 00:07:39.627 position:10% line:83% align:start
however, if you were to move
this blade another millimeter,

00:07:39.660 --> 00:07:42.563 position:16% line:83% align:start
it would certainly sever
a vital nerve in my neck.

00:07:42.596 --> 00:07:44.131 position:21% line:89% align:start
What a coincidence.

00:07:44.165 --> 00:07:47.935 position:10% line:83% align:start
Fortunately, this stab wound
does not appear to be fatal.

00:07:47.969 --> 00:07:50.470 position:24% line:83% align:start
What will you do?
It's your decision.

00:07:50.504 --> 00:07:52.974 position:21% line:83% align:start
Do you want to move
the scissors a bit or not?

00:07:53.007 --> 00:07:54.108 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Ungalo whimpers]

00:07:54.141 --> 00:07:57.511 position:13% line:83% align:start
But first, answer me this,
do you believe in gravity?

00:07:57.545 --> 00:07:58.746 position:10% line:89% align:start
Do you think there's a force

00:07:58.779 --> 00:08:01.082 position:7% line:83% align:start
that draws certain individuals
together?

00:08:01.115 --> 00:08:03.784 position:16% line:83% align:start
Personally, this moment
has made me a believer.

00:08:03.818 --> 00:08:06.454 position:21% line:83% align:start
You are not capable
of killing me.

00:08:06.486 --> 00:08:07.555 position:21% line:89% align:start
You are here because

00:08:07.588 --> 00:08:10.291 position:19% line:83% align:start
my gravitational pull
led you to me.

00:08:10.324 --> 00:08:11.525 position:24% line:83% align:start
Don't you see that
you shouldn't be

00:08:11.559 --> 00:08:14.428 position:21% line:83% align:start
wasting your energy
on useless drugs?

00:08:14.462 --> 00:08:16.130 position:24% line:83% align:start
No, you should be
using your energy

00:08:16.163 --> 00:08:17.565 position:16% line:89% align:start
on something much wiser.

00:08:18.199 --> 00:08:19.934 position:35% line:83% align:start
[whimpers]
Fuck this!

00:08:19.967 --> 00:08:20.634 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gunshots]

00:08:22.003 --> 00:08:23.170 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:08:23.204 --> 00:08:25.606 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:08:27.308 --> 00:08:28.576 position:13% line:89% align:start
From the looks of things,

00:08:28.609 --> 00:08:31.479 position:24% line:83% align:start
where it pertains
to who your father really is

00:08:31.512 --> 00:08:33.781 position:27% line:83% align:start
the three of you
are left in the dark.

00:08:33.814 --> 00:08:35.983 position:21% line:83% align:start
But that won't last
much longer.

00:08:36.017 --> 00:08:38.252 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:08:44.959 --> 00:08:47.028 position:30% line:83% align:start
Now that we've
been brought together,

00:08:47.061 --> 00:08:49.663 position:7% line:83% align:start
you will understand everything
soon enough.

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:55.169 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:09:07.982 --> 00:09:09.617 position:27% line:89% align:start
[rain pattering]

00:09:12.053 --> 00:09:13.020 position:24% line:89% align:start
[old man groaning]

00:09:15.389 --> 00:09:19.060 position:16% line:89% align:start
Oh, thank you very much.

00:09:19.093 --> 00:09:20.027 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm fine.

00:09:20.061 --> 00:09:21.530 position:21% line:89% align:start
Sorry to bother you.

00:09:21.562 --> 00:09:22.730 position:27% line:89% align:start
This is nothing.

00:09:22.763 --> 00:09:25.833 position:16% line:83% align:start
Just an old knee injury
from my carpentry days.

00:09:25.866 --> 00:09:28.736 position:30% line:83% align:start
When it rains,
my joints start to twinge.

00:09:28.769 --> 00:09:31.005 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Weather]
When it rains your knee hurts.

00:09:31.038 --> 00:09:32.139 position:35% line:89% align:start
Sure does.

00:09:33.140 --> 00:09:35.276 position:19% line:83% align:start
Thanks for showing me
some kindness.

00:09:36.677 --> 00:09:37.711 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia]
Stop getting into

00:09:37.745 --> 00:09:40.381 position:10% line:83% align:start
random strangers' business,
Weather.

00:09:40.414 --> 00:09:42.551 position:19% line:83% align:start
We're still fugitives,
remember?

00:09:42.583 --> 00:09:44.785 position:19% line:83% align:start
Our faces are blasted
all over the news.

00:09:44.819 --> 00:09:46.821 position:10% line:89% align:start
The geezer might report us.

00:09:46.854 --> 00:09:48.557 position:7% line:89% align:start
Our best bet is to steal a car

00:09:48.589 --> 00:09:50.891 position:7% line:83% align:start
and get the hell out of Dodge
immediately.

00:09:50.925 --> 00:09:52.126 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Weather]
No stolen cars.

00:09:52.159 --> 00:09:54.728 position:24% line:83% align:start
It'll be too easy
for them to track us.

00:09:54.762 --> 00:09:56.597 position:5% line:89% align:start
And then we'll never lose them.

00:09:56.630 --> 00:09:58.732 position:24% line:83% align:start
Chasing the priest
would become impossible.

00:09:58.766 --> 00:10:01.769 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're not suggesting
we take the bus, are you?

00:10:01.802 --> 00:10:04.573 position:10% line:83% align:start
How long are we supposed to
wait till the next one comes?

00:10:04.605 --> 00:10:07.509 position:13% line:83% align:start
-[old man] Oh, hey fellas.
-[both gasp]

00:10:07.542 --> 00:10:09.343 position:19% line:83% align:start
[old man] You thinking
of taking the bus?

00:10:09.376 --> 00:10:11.745 position:27% line:83% align:start
It won't be here
for another hour.

00:10:11.779 --> 00:10:14.482 position:13% line:83% align:start
How about I give you boys
a ride on my truck?

00:10:14.516 --> 00:10:16.283 position:19% line:83% align:start
You'll have to hop in
the back though.

00:10:16.317 --> 00:10:19.386 position:10% line:83% align:start
Maybe it's because you were
so kind to me earlier,

00:10:19.420 --> 00:10:21.622 position:27% line:83% align:start
but I'm feeling
better than ever.

00:10:21.655 --> 00:10:24.458 position:21% line:83% align:start
The pain in my knees
was awful moments ago,

00:10:24.492 --> 00:10:26.427 position:10% line:89% align:start
but it's miraculously gone.

00:10:26.460 --> 00:10:28.796 position:30% line:83% align:start
The sky feels
so refreshing, too.

00:10:28.829 --> 00:10:29.463 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh.

00:10:29.497 --> 00:10:31.665 position:19% line:89% align:start
[gentle bright music]

00:10:35.469 --> 00:10:36.971 position:21% line:89% align:start
[breathing heavily]

00:10:37.638 --> 00:10:39.206 position:24% line:89% align:start
Weather Forecast.

00:10:43.144 --> 00:10:46.847 position:16% line:83% align:start
Call it luck. We should
take his offer, Anastasia.

