00:12:01.255 --> 00:12:03.692 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whooshing]

00:12:03.724 --> 00:12:06.595 position:24% line:83% align:start
You sure? I still
see something darting around.

00:12:06.628 --> 00:12:08.963 position:33% line:83% align:start
Yeah, well.
I got this one for sure.

00:12:10.097 --> 00:12:12.099 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[groaning]
-[Anastasia] But what the hell

00:12:12.132 --> 00:12:13.334 position:30% line:89% align:start
is this thing?

00:12:13.367 --> 00:12:15.302 position:21% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music]

00:12:24.812 --> 00:12:26.280 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[groaning]
-Be on the alert,

00:12:26.313 --> 00:12:27.181 position:24% line:89% align:start
Weather Forecast.

00:12:27.214 --> 00:12:29.783 position:30% line:83% align:start
The Stand User
