00:12:37.224 --> 00:12:39.994 position:10% line:83% align:start
If it's not him, it must be
someone else in the area.

00:12:40.027 --> 00:12:42.363 position:7% line:83% align:start
Just like you're able to sense
where Jolyne is going,

00:12:42.396 --> 00:12:44.666 position:27% line:83% align:start
maybe the priest
can sense us getting closer

00:12:44.699 --> 00:12:47.569 position:13% line:83% align:start
