to stop us from getting to him.

00:12:47.602 --> 00:12:49.370 position:13% line:83% align:start
Now, who the hell are you?
Tell us!

00:12:49.403 --> 00:12:51.238 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Pinocchio] You...
You really shouldn't do that.

00:12:51.272 --> 00:12:53.240 position:16% line:83% align:start
