00:12:56.043 --> 00:12:56.777 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hm.

00:12:57.344 --> 00:12:58.713 position:33% line:89% align:start
Is that so?

00:12:58.747 --> 00:13:01.015 position:27% line:83% align:start
