00:13:12.159 --> 00:13:13.127 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:13:14.729 --> 00:13:16.897 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[Pinocchio] Whoa.
-[Anastasia grunts]

00:13:16.930 --> 00:13:19.567 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Pinocchio] My bad, man.
So sorry about that.

00:13:19.601 --> 00:13:21.536 position:7% line:89% align:start
I swear it wasn't on purpose.

00:13:21.569 --> 00:13:23.103 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia] You son of a...

00:13:23.137 --> 00:13:26.675 position:13% line:83% align:start
Ah, honestly, my nose just
