wasn't exactly a complete lie.

00:13:37.652 --> 00:13:40.321 position:13% line:83% align:start
So basically, I might not
be working with somebody,

00:13:40.354 --> 00:13:43.157 position:19% line:83% align:start
but that doesn't mean
that I'm alone necessarily.

00:13:43.190 --> 00:13:44.858 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:13:44.892 --> 00:13:48.929 position:19% line:83% align:start
