being so violent?

00:13:56.170 --> 00:13:58.305 position:21% line:83% align:start
It feels kinda weird
saying this about myself,

00:13:58.339 --> 00:14:00.775 position:33% line:83% align:start
but I think
I'm a pretty good guy.

00:14:00.809 --> 00:14:02.811 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm definitely nice
to children, at least.

00:14:02.843 --> 00:14:04.713 position:35% line:83% align:start
Actually,
I might have been your friend

00:14:04.746 --> 00:14:06.715 position:19% line:89% align:start
when you were younger.

00:14:06.748 --> 00:14:09.450 position:19% line:83% align:start
Oh yeah, that's right,
speaking of friends,

00:14:09.483 --> 00:14:12.319 position:7% line:83% align:start
I think the seven of them are
hiding around here somewhere.

00:14:12.353 --> 00:14:15.856 position:7% line:83% align:start
I saw three of the seven guys
a minute ago. See?

00:14:15.889 --> 00:14:17.958 position:16% line:83% align:start
Someone's been snacking
on that apple over there.

00:14:18.392 --> 00:14:19.860 position:33% line:89% align:start
[both gasp]

00:14:19.893 --> 00:14:22.731 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ominous music]

00:14:22.764 --> 00:14:24.131 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia]
Hey, Weather, you seeing this?

00:14:24.164 --> 00:14:25.633 position:13% line:89% align:start
What the fuck is going on?

00:14:27.401 --> 00:14:28.503 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:14:31.138 --> 00:14:33.508 position:24% line:83% align:start
Just so you know,
that apple isn't poisonous.

00:14:33.541 --> 00:14:35.008 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's okay to eat.

00:14:35.042 --> 00:14:37.344 position:24% line:83% align:start
Yeah, but the one
Snow White ate was poisonous.

00:14:37.378 --> 00:14:40.381 position:5% line:83% align:start
No, she didn't actually eat it,
she choked on a piece of it.

00:14:40.414 --> 00:14:42.517 position:30% line:83% align:start
So technically
she didn't digest it.

00:14:43.651 --> 00:14:45.152 position:33% line:83% align:start
But, I mean,
who would eat an apple

00:14:45.185 --> 00:14:47.187 position:27% line:83% align:start
from an old lady
they didn't know?

00:14:47.221 --> 00:14:49.189 position:16% line:83% align:start
Even on Valentine's day,
we're careful about

00:14:49.223 --> 00:14:50.924 position:30% line:83% align:start
