we put in our mouths.

00:14:50.958 --> 00:14:52.326 position:30% line:83% align:start
Although it's
that carelessness of hers

00:14:52.359 --> 00:14:54.796 position:7% line:83% align:start
that makes you want to protect
her with your whole life.

00:14:54.829 --> 00:14:57.732 position:30% line:89% align:start
[eerie music]

00:14:57.766 --> 00:15:00.134 position:35% line:83% align:start
Holy shit!
ow many of you are there?

00:15:00.167 --> 00:15:02.236 position:10% line:83% align:start
