who's your favorite character?

00:15:09.544 --> 00:15:11.345 position:10% line:89% align:start
Maybe it was little ol' me?

00:15:11.378 --> 00:15:14.348 position:10% line:83% align:start
Personally, I've got a thing
for The Terminator T-1000,

00:15:14.381 --> 00:15:15.850 position:30% line:83% align:start
that guy ain't
on the truck though.

00:15:15.884 --> 00:15:17.685 position:7% line:89% align:start
Me and my bro like Chewbacca.

00:15:17.719 --> 00:15:19.486 position:13% line:89% align:start
And The Elephant Man, too.

00:15:19.521 --> 00:15:22.022 position:21% line:83% align:start
But no matter what,
our Princess Snow White

00:15:22.055 --> 00:15:24.526 position:10% line:89% align:start
