00:15:24.559 --> 00:15:25.727 position:16% line:89% align:start
[all dwarves] Heigh-ho!

00:15:25.760 --> 00:15:27.394 position:19% line:83% align:start
We know all the rumors
about us,

00:15:27.428 --> 00:15:29.329 position:21% line:83% align:start
