sneak into a girl's panties

00:15:29.363 --> 00:15:31.866 position:10% line:83% align:start
and do dirty things to her,
but they're lies!

00:15:31.900 --> 00:15:34.435 position:10% line:83% align:start
Our relationship is platonic
all the way!

00:15:34.468 --> 00:15:35.936 position:21% line:89% align:start
[all dwarves] Yeah!

00:15:36.336 --> 00:15:37.672 position:33% line:89% align:start
[soft grunt]

00:15:40.340 --> 00:15:42.644 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia]
These... these guys are...

00:15:42.677 --> 00:15:44.077 position:21% line:89% align:start
