00:16:08.068 --> 00:16:09.637 position:16% line:89% align:start
You hear that, Weather?

00:16:09.671 --> 00:16:12.574 position:16% line:83% align:start
Are these little freaks
who I think they are?

00:16:12.607 --> 00:16:14.642 position:30% line:83% align:start
Does this mean
they've been brought to life?

00:16:14.676 --> 00:16:16.644 position:10% line:89% align:start
