00:16:16.678 --> 00:16:17.612 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:16:18.445 --> 00:16:19.213 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hm.

00:16:19.781 --> 00:16:21.081 position:33% line:89% align:start
[crunching]

00:16:24.351 --> 00:16:25.820 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh?

00:16:25.854 --> 00:16:29.958 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hey. Who are you a fan of?
Do you like me?

00:16:29.990 --> 00:16:32.660 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry,
but I don't know who you are.

00:16:32.694 --> 00:16:34.829 position:7% line:89% align:start
