00:16:34.863 --> 00:16:36.230 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:16:36.263 --> 00:16:39.233 position:5% line:83% align:start
What the hell, Weather? Did you
really just take my stuff?

00:16:39.266 --> 00:16:41.569 position:21% line:83% align:start
I was in the middle
of reading that, you know!

00:16:41.603 --> 00:16:42.336 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia] Give it back!

00:16:43.437 --> 00:16:44.204 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:16:44.238 --> 00:16:46.106 position:13% line:89% align:start
