00:16:47.140 --> 00:16:48.475 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hey, Anastasia?

00:16:48.510 --> 00:16:49.544 position:24% line:89% align:start
Where did you go?

00:16:50.712 --> 00:16:53.013 position:7% line:89% align:start
