Can you hear me say "stop"?

00:17:05.492 --> 00:17:07.662 position:33% line:83% align:start
What is it?
What's going on, Weather?

00:17:08.696 --> 00:17:10.430 position:21% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music]

00:17:11.164 --> 00:17:12.534 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia gasps]

00:17:13.601 --> 00:17:16.236 position:16% line:89% align:start
