00:17:29.951 --> 00:17:31.686 position:19% line:89% align:start
I knew you were a fan.

00:17:32.085 --> 00:17:34.022 position:35% line:89% align:start
No! Shit!

00:17:34.054 --> 00:17:36.490 position:30% line:83% align:start
At this rate,
it'll get caught in the tires.

00:17:36.524 --> 00:17:39.192 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, Weather, make him
stop the truck. [gasps]

00:17:41.863 --> 00:17:43.163 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:17:43.196 --> 00:17:45.132 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ominous music]

00:17:46.801 --> 00:17:49.069 position:21% line:89% align:start
Wait, could he be...

