00:17:58.713 --> 00:18:00.748 position:27% line:89% align:start
[pensive music]

00:18:03.585 --> 00:18:04.451 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia grunts]

00:18:13.962 --> 00:18:17.297 position:27% line:83% align:start
I made an airbag
with Weather Forecast.

00:18:17.899 --> 00:18:19.433 position:30% line:89% align:start
You all right?

00:18:19.466 --> 00:18:22.537 position:13% line:83% align:start
