00:18:22.570 --> 00:18:23.538 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:18:23.571 --> 00:18:26.406 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm pretty sure
this is a Stand User's doing,

00:18:26.440 --> 00:18:28.009 position:24% line:83% align:start
but I have no idea
why you were

00:18:28.042 --> 00:18:29.711 position:33% line:83% align:start
the only one
who was targeted.

00:18:29.744 --> 00:18:32.179 position:10% line:83% align:start
If I were to wager a guess,
I'd say it has something

00:18:32.212 --> 00:18:34.616 position:16% line:83% align:start
to do with my ignorance
of these characters.

00:18:34.649 --> 00:18:36.017 position:16% line:89% align:start
That must be the reason.

00:18:36.050 --> 00:18:38.418 position:19% line:83% align:start
-[Pinocchio grunting]
-Come on, Weather!

00:18:38.452 --> 00:18:40.822 position:5% line:83% align:start
