or can you just not see me?

00:18:40.855 --> 00:18:43.156 position:21% line:83% align:start
And is that my body
that's limp in your arms?

00:18:43.190 --> 00:18:44.626 position:30% line:89% align:start
Everyone okay?

00:18:44.659 --> 00:18:45.292 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dwarves] Yeah!

00:18:45.325 --> 00:18:46.728 position:13% line:89% align:start
But where's the princess?

00:18:46.761 --> 00:18:47.762 position:27% line:89% align:start
Is she okay too?

00:18:47.795 --> 00:18:49.063 position:13% line:89% align:start
She flew out of the truck

00:18:49.097 --> 00:18:50.230 position:19% line:83% align:start
and got thrown towards
that burger shop.

00:18:50.263 --> 00:18:51.498 position:27% line:89% align:start
Let's help her!

00:18:51.532 --> 00:18:54.102 position:35% line:83% align:start
Hey, look!
Anybody know those guys?

00:18:54.134 --> 00:18:55.435 position:35% line:83% align:start
[dwarf 2]
I know 'em,

00:18:55.469 --> 00:18:57.038 position:7% line:83% align:start
but it ain't like I'm friends
with them or anything.

00:18:57.071 --> 00:18:58.506 position:24% line:89% align:start
They're Japanese!

00:18:58.539 --> 00:19:01.341 position:7% line:83% align:start
They've got some cool designs
